## 7. Heritage items not recognised

Where the entity holds heritage items that are not recognised as assets (because fair value cannot be reliably measured, or for other reasons permitted by IPSAS 45.71), the existence of those items is disclosed in the heritage register and the reasons for non-recognition are documented per item.

## 8. Restrictions

Restrictions on disposal, use, or location attaching to recognised heritage items are documented on the heritage register and aggregated in the register summary report.

